							"path": ["api", "v1", "chat", "completions"]
						},
						"description": "OpenAI-compatible chat completion endpoint.\n\n**Body:**\n- `messages` (required) — array of {role, content}\n- `stream` (optional) — boolean, enables SSE streaming\n- `web_search` (optional) — boolean, enables web search context\n- `model` (optional) — override model\n- `max_tokens` (optional) — 1-8192\n- `temperature` (optional) — 0-2"
					}
				},
